org.jppf.utils.stats

Class JPPFStatisticsHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jppf.utils.stats.JPPFStatisticsHelper

  • public final class JPPFStatisticsHelper
extends Object
    This helper class holds the constants definitions for the labels of the statistics snapshots used in JPPF, along with utility methods.
